01:29:44.884 --> 01:29:54.904
Incoming livestream: Thus, the story I'm going to tell is diff to hypothesis to harness, and the trick is that we will augment open source diffs with two other signals, binaries and OS logs.


607
01:29:55.034 --> 01:30:00.404
